$pic_text[27] = "<TR><TD width=90><FONT face='Comic Sans MS' color=#800000 size=2><center><B>Picture 27</B><BR>".
    "<A href='http://www.bbsvp.com.br/prefeitura.vassouras/governo.htm'><IMG SRC='images/pic27bis_small.jpg' border=1 alt='Vassouras city'><font size=1><br>click on coat of arms to access Vassouras's city official website</a><BR><BR><BR><a href='?num=127'><IMG SRC='images/pic27ter_small.jpg' border=0><br>An article of Vassouras's newspaper</a></center></font></TD><TD width=458><IMG SRC='images/pic27_big.jpg' border=1></TD><TD width=458><P align=left><FONT color=#800000 size=2>Tim, Anna, David and Eduardo went to visit Vassouras city in May/2000, that means 'brooms' in English. Marcos was the our driver. <BR>This city is located in the highland area of the Rio de Janeiro state and it was very used by the Portuguese former-emperor as well as Brazilian oligarchy in the nineteenth century.<br>The main picture is taken outside the disused railway station. The visit included several tourist points of this nice city, and later we went to a local rodízio-type restaurant (smaller picture).</TD></TR>";

